31
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,272
Halen we 't?

32
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,598
We halen 't.

33
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,309
De bond van dokwerkers.

34
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:59,790
Mijn broer is belangrijk voor me.

35
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:02,553
We moeten iemand vinden.

36
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:05,552
