136
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,911
Let goed op.

137
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:43,075
Mensen, stem op Donnelly.

138
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:48,510
Kom maar.
- Dat kan ik zelf wel.

139
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,556
Hulp van Donnelly.

140
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,517
Wegwezen, knul.

141
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:56,314
Kom, moeder.
