'n paardedinges.

722
01:12:46,520 --> 01:12:48,158
Niks aan de hand.

723
01:12:49,280 --> 01:12:51,510
Even op adem komen.

724
01:12:52,840 --> 01:12:56,230
Geen beweging,
of Dodds is wijlen.

725
01:12:56,320 --> 01:12:58,550
